content: I do not have personal preferences or favorites. however, some performers are widely acclaimed for their talents and have become popular due to their unique styles, exceptional skills, and mesmerizing performances. people like meryl streep, denzel washington, hugh jackman, lin-manuel miranda, beyoncé, and many others are highly regarded in their respective fields. whether it's theater, film, music, or dance, there are many talented artists out there who continue to inspire and captivate audiences with their work.
